{"id":40594,"title":"[Digital Pen & Paper&reg; technology to manage clinical risk and to prevent medical malpractice claims].","abstract":"The use of innovative technologies in the health sector can be a key element in clinical risk management. In order to reduce errors in medical recording and to provide medico-legal evidence, Digital Pen & Paper technology has been adopted by medical staff of a hospital in Milan. The Authors introduce the first results of this trial: notable advantages have been reported in compilation, transmission and storage of medical records. Furthermore, this technology could provide evidence in evaluating medical malpractice claims. ","date":"2014-07-10","categories":"Digestive System Diseases","split":"test","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25008227","annotations":[{"name":"Health","weight":0.620592,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health"},{"name":"Technology","weight":0.618886,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Technology"},{"name":"Medicine","weight":0.475548,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medicine"},{"name":"Hospital","weight":0.452096,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hospital"},{"name":"Management","weight":0.435489,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Management"},{"name":"Risk management","weight":0.370736,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Risk_management"},{"name":"Risk","weight":0.351631,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Risk"},{"name":"Trial","weight":0.313385,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trial"},{"name":"Milan","weight":0.268656,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Milan"},{"name":"Evidence","weight":0.20613,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evidence"},{"name":"Medical record","weight":0.141289,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medical_record"},{"name":"Paper","weight":0.0805305,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paper"},{"name":